Aníbal Troilo

CD-Discography of 531 Aníbal Troilo recordings and several "inéditos".

 

Probably still missing:

  • La retrechera, Habanera, 1953, canta: Aída Luz, Ssello Pampa
  • Patio mío, Tango, 1953, canta: Aída Luz, Sello Pampa (Troilo as orchestra unverified)

 

In case you found missing or wrong information, or you might be able to help finding missing tracks - any feedback is very much welcomed! You may get in contact with me, or leave your comment at the end of this page.

If you are interested in one of the CDs mentioned take a look at Tango-CDs.com.

Please find more information about Aníbal Troilo at Todotango.com.
